author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Silicone caulking tips…I’m using Latasil color-matching silicone. I apply it with the Newborn 930-GTD caulking gun which is specifically for silicone. I lightly spray the joint then use the DAP caulking tool with a lot of pressure. This makes the silicone tight against the tile and door threshold 🔥#caulking #tilefloor #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
title: Silicone Caulking Tips - #shorts #caulking #homerepairtutor
